        static lejos.geom.Line line0
        one line of the map of the robot course. The course consists of a closed chain of straight lines. Thus every next line starts where the last line ends and the last line ends where the first line starts. This documentation for line0 hold for all lines.

      • map

        static lejos.geom.Line[] map
        map of the robot course. The course consists of a closed chain of straight lines. Thus every next line starts where the last line ends and the last line ends where the first line starts. All above defined lines are bundled in this array and to form the course map.
